<plot>With the power of the beast comes the hunger, a hunger that cannot always be controlled. Here are the stories of three men whose lives are changed by the caprice of lycanthropy. There's the mob boss who is cursed by an ancient evil, a nebbish man who craves power he's never had and will do anything to get it, and the descendent of a certain Dr. Jeckyll, who has finally reconstituted the formula created by his great grandfather.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?650751</url></doc>
